<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Effect:</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
-Extends buff length by 15%<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Restrictions:</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
